{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">DRAKE is an isometric-like Action RPG featuring non-linear level exploration and a unique interactive story. Set in a densely crafted Space Western world, it draws inspiration from beloved series like The Mandalorian, Firefly, and Trigun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game delivers a modern twist on classic RPGs. Our narrative approach provides each player with a unique story to experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735880/extras/Gif_01.gif?t=1733219801\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DRAKE IS AN ACTION ROLE-PLAYING GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your choices influence not only the state of the world and unfolding events but also the personality of your protagonist. This alters gameplay, offering truly immersive character progression and role-playing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735880/extras/Gif_02.gif?t=1733219801\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DRAKE IS A ROAD ADVENTURE</h2>Every major point on the map is more than just a destination; it is part of this planet's backstory and a pivotal moment in your journey. Decide which faction aligns with your worldview and with whom you will join forces as your journey continues.<br><br>What will be your path, Space Cowboy? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1735880/extras/Chars2.png?t=1733219801\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DRAKE IS A SPACE WESTERN WORLD</h2>A brand new adventure awaits you, featuring:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CRPG game with a 3D isometric action and consequential choices;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A brand new story filled w